{"tid":919611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烏俄恐爆發全面戰爭  美英法40戰機北海演習  聯手應對全球威脅","createTime":"2018-11-28T07:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T06:55:20.000Z","uid":141060,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"a957422148787b19b368f8a91d99f2aefb366e8a","tid":919611,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:26:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181128/bkn-20181128124111694-1128_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181128%2Fbkn-20181128124111694-1128_00912_001.html&d=FCE3QmlYR159ByaDNFjom8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d5df71fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181128/bkn-20181128124111694-1128_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181128/photo/bkn-20181128124111694-1128_00912_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181128%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181128124111694-1128_00912_001_01p.jpg&h=cef8fcff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181128/photo/bkn-20181128124111694-1128_00912_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181128%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181128124111694-1128_00912_001_02p.jpg&h=f775c03a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烏俄恐爆發全面戰爭之際，美國、英國及法國於周二（27日）出動超過40架戰機在北海上空演習，作為應對全球威脅的「保證政策」。英軍指安全環境正在變化，俄羅斯挑戰國際秩序，演習有助與盟友準備好應對威脅。<br />\n<br />\n參與演習的戰機分別是美國空軍的F-15E、英國皇家空軍的F-35B及歐洲颱風，以及法國空軍的疾風式，它們從英國萊肯希思空軍基地出發，在北海及英倫海峽上空演習。美軍指這有改善盟友之間的協同作戰能力，並展示美方對歐洲安全的承諾，也有利第4代與第5代戰機的協同能力及整合。<br />\n<br />\n演習過往只有英美兩國的戰機，而今次是法國首次參與。英國皇家空軍准將阿特里奇（Jez Attridge）形容，空軍屬於「保證政策」。他說：「我們見到環境正在改變，以及俄羅斯挑戰以規則為基礎的國際秩序，因此我們要做好準備及隨時候命。」"},{"pid":"48a25e788d9b573c98bbdf0d336f6a39256576e6","tid":919611,"uid":158613,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:33:20.000Z","msg":"法國總統：淨係法國自己都夠做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c42d1939db0cde60eb5c084d0ba2248a3ed0351","tid":919611,"uid":121146,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:36:03.000Z","msg":"俄佬而家淆撚哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5123ee41b1195e71c3c3f42133976aff2fd689","tid":919611,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"德國呢？"},{"pid":"4a125e686b0fad10fc3e5ac03db5fdec0da7b7f5","tid":919611,"uid":123859,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7d5123ee41b1195e71c3c3f42133976aff2fd689","tid":919611,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"德國呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牛刀洗撚斬on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e427887146245241cee64d2fc27a766139fe85","tid":919611,"uid":11719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:39:42.000Z","msg":"美國唔出F35，今次俾英國威晒啦"},{"pid":"e8958000c1973139452d7c0ece5e295190789181","tid":919611,"uid":38041,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"因為李卓人落選 本土派應當悔改<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28160afcdec21180374fe10ba7c517a058c0b798","tid":919611,"uid":52148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a12